Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:07.81,Default,van,0,0,0,,O my God, I am heartily sorry for having offended thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:07.81,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,我 主の限りなく嫌い給う罪を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.59,Default,van,0,0,0,,and I detest all my sins because of thy just punishments,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.59,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,限りなく愛すべき御父に背きしを深く悔み奉る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:15.00,花語製作通用-ja,,0,0,0,,本字幕由✿花語&千夏字幕組✿共同製作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:18.11,Default,van,0,0,0,,but most of all because they offend thee, my God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:18.11,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,御子イエズス キリストの流し給える御血の功徳によりて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:22.87,Default,van,0,0,0,,who art all good and deserving of all my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:22.87,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,わが罪を赦し給え 聖寵の助けをもって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:27.19,Default,van,0,0,0,,I firmly resolve, with the help of thy grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:27.19,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,今より心を改め 再び罪を犯して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:31.72,Default,van,0,0,0,,to sin no more and avoid the near occasions of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:31.72,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,御心に背くことあるまじと決心し奉る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:33.72,Default,van,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:33.72,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,アーメン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:47.91,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:47.91,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,無事だったんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.73,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Shall I make some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.73,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,コーヒー入れようか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.18,Default,av,0,0,0,,You were here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.18,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ずっとここに?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:01.64,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Yeah. I planned to stay awake until you got back, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:01.64,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,うん アヴィリオが戻るまで起きてるつもりだったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:03.18,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Is Fango...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:03.18,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ファンゴは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.12,Default,avi,0,0,0,,I screwed up. With Fango, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.12,通用720日文-ja,avi,0,0,0,,やり損なった ファンゴはな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.84,Default,av,0,0,0,,Vanno Clemente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.84,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ヴァンノ クレメンテ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:26.26,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Are you working with Orco?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:26.26,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,オルコの犬か?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:29.75,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Did you kill Vanno?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:29.75,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前がヴァンノをやったのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.73,Default,av,0,0,0,,If I had, I'd be out of town by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.73,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,だったらこの町を出てる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Bring me Serpente's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.73,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,セルペンテの死体を持って来い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.06,Default,nero,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.06,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,さもなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.00,Default,cor,0,0,0,,So where is his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.00,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,その死体はどこに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.12,Default,av,0,0,0,,It wasn't you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.12,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,お前じゃないよな
