Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.84,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.84,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:43.86,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Cerotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:43.86,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,チェロット
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.38,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Corteo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.38,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,コルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.11,Default,cer,0,0,0,,What do you want? I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.11,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,うんだよ 今忙しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.17,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Last night... where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.17,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,昨日の夜 どこに行った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.38,Default,cer,0,0,0,,D-Drinking with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.38,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,友達と飲んでたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.46,Default,cer,0,0,0,,All night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.46,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,一晩中な
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:59.12,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You were near Fango's apartment with Avilio and Vanno, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:59.12,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ達と ファンゴのところに行ったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:03:59.84,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.66,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,いたっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:03.96,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, but I didn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:03.96,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,だけど 俺はなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.40,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Avilio is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.40,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリオが君を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.98,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Nero ordered him to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.98,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ネロから指示されたらしいよ 君を殺せって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.81,Default,cer,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.81,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ま 待ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.81,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.81,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,一体 どういうことだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:21.15,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Last night, Vanno of the Vanetti family was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:21.15,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,昨日の夜 バネッティファミリーのヴァンノが殺された
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:26.27,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You're the one behind it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:26.27,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,本当のところ 君がやったんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.93,Default,cer,0,0,0,,You gotta be joking! You've got the wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.93,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ふざけんなよ あれは俺じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.61,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.61,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,いや だから あれは...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.70,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.70,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.52,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.52,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,と...こうしあいらね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:53.01,Default,cer,0,0,0,,This is serious trouble. I gotta make tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:53.01,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,マジでやべぇ さっさと逃げねと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:56.92,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Cerotto. I haven't told Avilio about this bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:56.92,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,チェロット アヴィリオにここのことは教えてない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.15,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.15,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,何があったか話してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.28,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I might be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.28,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,力になれるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.78,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.78,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,俺はやってない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.87,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I really didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.87,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,本当にやってないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.04,Default,cook,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.04,通用720日文-ja,cook,0,0,0,,あ あの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.39,Default,or,0,0,0,,Not enough butter in the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.39,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,ソースのバターが足りねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.31,Default,cook,0,0,0,,D-Don Orco, last time, you said there was too much butter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.31,通用720日文-ja,cook,0,0,0,,ドン ドンオルコ 前はバターが強すぎると
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.39,Default,or,0,0,0,,So you just put in less butter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.39,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,だからバターを減らしたってのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:51.60,Default,or,0,0,0,,Lasagna is about harmony, you know. It's not math.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:51.60,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,ラザニアってのはハーモニーだ 算数じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:55.43,Default,or,0,0,0,,Just adding and subtracting won't get you the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:55.43,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,足したり引いたりしただけじゃ 答えは出ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.33,Default,cook,0,0,0,,Don! Great Don Orco...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.33,通用720日文-ja,cook,0,0,0,,ドン 偉大なるドンオルコ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.46,Default,cook,0,0,0,,Please, give me another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.46,通用720日文-ja,cook,0,0,0,,もう一度私にチャンスを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:04.79,Default,or,0,0,0,,You didn't feed us lasagna. You fed us pig slop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:04.79,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,この皿に載ってるのはラザニアじゃんぇ 豚の餌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.77,Default,or,0,0,0,,I'll ask, just to be sure. Does anyone like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.77,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,念の為に聞くが 美味かった奴はいるか?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.22,Default,or,0,0,0,,You heard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.22,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,だそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.54,Default,or,0,0,0,,Give my regards to the pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.54,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,豚によろしくな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.97,Overlap,cook,0,0,0,,Please! Give me one more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.97,通用720日文-ja,cook,0,0,0,,{\an8}お願いします もう一度チャンスを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:21.77,Default,cook,0,0,0,,D-Don Orco! Please! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:21.77,通用720日文-ja,cook,0,0,0,,ドン ドンオルコ お願い もう一度だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.97,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Hey, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.97,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ちっと見てくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.90,Default,or,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Got some bug bites, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.90,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,どうした 虫にでも刺されたか?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.26,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Nope. Someone tried to run a hit on me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.26,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,うんにゃ 昨日やられかけたんだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:39.12,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Wasn't anyone I know, but it's gotta be Vanetti who arranged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:39.12,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,見ねぇ顔だったが あれ絶対裏にバネッティがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.49,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Let's toss a little dynamite onto their turf, take out the whole...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.49,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,なぁ 奴等のシマにダイナマイトでも放り込んでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.42,Default,or,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.98,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,うるせぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.99,Default,or,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof that it was the Vanettis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.99,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,バネッティだっていう証拠はあんのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.39,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Who else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.39,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,それ奴等しかいねぇだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.63,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I've been taking huge chunks of their turf, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.80,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺様にこっそりシマを取られてるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:03.26,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, you've all been here, stuffing your faces like pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:03.26,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,あんたらがここで豚みたいに飯食ってる間にな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.68,Default,co,0,0,0,,Why, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.68,通用720日文-ja,co,0,0,0,,この
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.70,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Not enough butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.70,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,バターが足りねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:14.78,Default,or,0,0,0,,The Galassias want to see us make nice with the Vanettis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:14.78,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,ガラッシアはうちとバネッティの手打ちを望んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:19.86,Default,or,0,0,0,,I'm not about to start a war over a few cuts on your stinking feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:19.86,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,おめぇのくせぇ足に傷がついたくらいで戦争はごめんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.37,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Whatever, I'll just do things my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.37,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,好きにやらせて貰うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.75,Default,fan,0,0,0,,By the way, anyone seen Serpente?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.75,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そうそう セルペンテ知らねか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.16,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,知らねな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.18,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.35,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Maybe one of Vanetti's guys seduced him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.35,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,バネッティのやつに寝取られちまったんじゃねぇの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.61,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.61,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ご馳走さん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:44.30,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Ottimo Orco... Some feeding trough you've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:44.30,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,オッティモ オルコか 大した餌場だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.67,Default,cer,0,0,0,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.67,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,あのやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.63,Default,or,0,0,0,,Let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.63,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,あいつはもういいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:53.09,Default,or,0,0,0,,As ostentatious as he's been, he's bound to have an enemy or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:53.09,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,あんだけ派手にやってれば 恨みを買うこともあるだろうしな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.35,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Yeah. I went to Fango's apartment with Avilio and Vanno,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.35,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ達とファンゴのアパートに行った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.74,Default,cer,0,0,0,,but all I did was offer Serpente some booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.74,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,でも俺はセルペンテの兄貴に酒を薦めただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.07,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What happened then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.07,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,その後どうしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:09.83,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I knew things had gotten bad, but I couldn't help getting curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:09.83,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,やばいのは分かっちゃいたが つい気になって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:28.40,Default,cer,0,0,0,,So I hailed a taxi and followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:28.40,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,俺はタクシーを拾って やつの車を追った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.57,Default,cor,0,0,0,,They took each other out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.57,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,相打ちってこと?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.68,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ヴァンノがアパートから運び出してた時にはま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:01.74,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he was still alive when Vanno carried him out of the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.74,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,まだ生きてたんだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.18,Default,cor,0,0,0,,But Serpente's corpse is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.18,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,でも セルペンテの死体は消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:05.96,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,このままだと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:09.56,Default,cor,0,0,0,,The way things are, it looks like you killed Vanno and helped Serpente escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:09.56,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,君がヴァンノを殺して セルペンテを逃がしたってことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.69,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Damn! I got greedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.69,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,チクショウ 欲かいちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.77,Default,cer,0,0,0,,No, no... I don't have time for this! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.77,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,だめだ こんことやってってる場合じゃねえ くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.36,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you got greedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.36,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,欲かいだってどういう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:24.91,Default,cer,0,0,0,,That's right. I need to tell Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:24.91,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,そうだ とりあえず 兄貴に話さねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.67,Default,cer,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.67,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ま 待って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.71,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I didn't kill Vanno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.71,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ヴァンノは俺が殺したんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.85,Default,av,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.85,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.72,Default,av,0,0,0,,Then what happened to Serpente's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.72,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,それじゃセルペンテの死体はどうした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.49,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I sold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.49,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,売った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.97,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I sold it to Scusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.97,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,スクーザに売っちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,Scusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.99,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,スクーザ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:58.61,Default,cer,0,0,0,,The Federal Bureau of Prohibition guy who showed up in town recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:58.61,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,最近 この町に来た連邦取締官だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.08,Default,av,0,0,0,,And he took the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.08,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,死体はそいつが持っていったのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.34,Default,av,0,0,0,,Take me to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.34,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,連れて行け
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:10.35,Default,av,0,0,0,,If it's not there, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:10.35,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そこになかったら お前を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.98,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,セルペンテの死体が表沙汰になっなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:17.71,Default,bar,0,0,0,,If word of Serpente's body gets out, it's going to cause a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.71,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,いろいろと面倒になるなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.00,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Oh, please. He killed our Vanno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.00,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,こっちはヴァンノやられてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.84,Default,tig,0,0,0,,It's an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.84,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,目には目をだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.26,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Nero. If he can't find the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.46,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ネロ 死体を見つけられなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.29,Default,bar,0,0,0,,what will you do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.29,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,やつをどうするつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.32,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.32,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,さなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.22,Default,tig,0,0,0,,They're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.22,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,出てきたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:40.14,Default,tig,0,0,0,,All right, show us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:40.14,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,さて 案内してもらうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.22,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Vanno's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.22,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ヴァンノが?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:46.35,Default,scu,0,0,0,,As far as we can tell, they took each other out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:46.35,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,状況を見た限り 相打ちでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.58,Default,scu,0,0,0,,But the fact of the matter is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.58,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,そのヴァンノに拉致されて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.90,Default,scu,0,0,0,,Vanno abducted and killed a member of the Orco family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.90,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,オルコファミリーの人間が殺されたわけです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.57,Default,ron,0,0,0,,That meddling idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.57,720通用注釋-ja,ron,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord1\pos(627,592.333)}沒事找事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.57,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,余計なことしてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.45,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Where's Serpente's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.45,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,セルペンテの死体は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:01.45,Default,scu,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I have it safely in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:01.45,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,ご安心ください 私のところでしかっり預かってますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.70,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Scusa! You really think you can blackmail the Vanettis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.70,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,スクーザ てめぇ バネッティを揺すろうってのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:06.98,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,ガンゾさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:11.60,Default,scu,0,0,0,,Mr. Ganzo. I understand your anger, but let's discuss this calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.24,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,まあ お気持ちは分かりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.60,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,ここは冷静に話し合いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.07,Default,fla,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.07,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,いくら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.42,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Hey, Frate! Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.42,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,おい フラテ お前が口出すことじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.58,Default,gan,0,0,0,,We don't need some kid's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.58,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ガキは黙ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.15,Default,ron,0,0,0,,What choice do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.15,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,仕方ないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:25.03,Default,ron,0,0,0,,If this gets out, it'll start a fight with the Orcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:25.03,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,表沙汰んなったら オルコと小競り合いになる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.97,Default,ron,0,0,0,,The Galassias aren't gonna stand for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.97,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,結果 ガラッシアも黙っちゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:35.06,Default,scu,0,0,0,,So, you'll buy it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:35.06,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,それでは 買っていただけるのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:39.13,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I prefer to keep things simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:39.13,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,俺はシンプルなやり方が好きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.64,Default,vin,0,0,0,,That's why I dislike this sort of haggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.64,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,だがらこういう駆け引きは好みじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.31,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.31,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,覚えとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.31,Default,vin,0,0,0,,First, bring the body here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.31,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,まず 死体をここに持ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.34,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Then we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.34,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,話はそっからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:59.97,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Is Serpente dead or not? We oughta just ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:59.97,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,セルペンテはやったのか やってねぇのか 直接聞けばいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.57,Default,gat,0,0,0,,Ask them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.57,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,直接?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.53,Default,gat,0,0,0,,At Vanetti's mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.53,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,バネッティの屋敷に?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:07.00,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Yeah. You got a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:07.00,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ほかにいい手があるか?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.78,Default,gat,0,0,0,,Don Orco doesn't want you starting trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.78,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,揉め事はドン オルコが許さねぇじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.80,Default,fan,0,0,0,,The old man won't be around much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.80,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,オヤジはもう長くねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.46,Default,fan,0,0,0,,It's my lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.46,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ついてるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.81,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:30.93,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.36,Default,cer,0,0,0,,This building is about to be demolished soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.36,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ここは近いうちに取り壊しになるんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.99,Default,cer,0,0,0,,It's the perfect place for Scusa's men to hide their stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.99,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,スクーザたちが押収した物を隠すりゃ お誂え向き
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.02,Default,cer,0,0,0,,That's the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.02,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,あの部屋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.05,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Let's get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.05,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,さっさと運び出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.42,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Kill Nero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.42,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ネロをやるだと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.31,Default,gan,0,0,0,,We don't even know for sure that Nero killed Serpente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.31,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,セルペンテやったのはネロだと決まったわけじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.61,Default,gan,0,0,0,,And we lost Vanno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.61,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,こっちはヴァンノやられてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:17.20,Default,ron,0,0,0,,How stupid do you have to be to kidnap someone and then get yourself killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:17.20,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,拉致一人で返り討ちに遭うさ 間抜けにもほどがある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:23.34,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Ganzo, calm down. You'll ruin your brain, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:23.34,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ガンゾ落ち着け 俺みたいに脳をやっちまうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.55,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Nothing good's happened since he came around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.55,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,こいつが来てからろくなことがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.93,Default,fla,0,0,0,,One of my brother's men was killed by Orco recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.93,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,この間 兄さんの手下がオルコにやられた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:34.41,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Vanno probably killed Serpente to get even,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:34.41,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,ヴァンノはその腹いせに セルペンテをやったんだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.66,Default,fla,0,0,0,,and I bet my brother knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.66,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,たぶん 兄さんも知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.68,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Either way, he's already made fools out of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.68,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,いずれにしろ ここまで虚仮にされたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.93,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I don't think Don Galassia will forgive Nero for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.93,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ドン ガラッシアがネロを許すは思えない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.68,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,俺らが奴をやれないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:50.62,Default,ron,0,0,0,,If we don't kill him, the Galassias will just get personally involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.62,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,直接ガラッシアが乗り込んで来るだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.38,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I think—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.38,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ここは...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.60,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I see what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.60,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,お前が言いたいことは分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.10,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Leave Nero to me. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.10,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ネロは俺に任せろ いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:03.36,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:03.36,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,まぁ そういうことであれば どうぞ ご自由に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:07.06,Default,ron,0,0,0,,But you're the one who'll have to wipe your kid's ass for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:07.06,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ただ息子の尻はご自分で拭いてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.59,Default,gan,0,0,0,,It's about time you outgrew diapers, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.59,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,てめぇもオムツを外しとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.32,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Ganzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.32,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ガンゾ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.14,Default,gan,0,0,0,,That little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.14,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,あのガキ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.12,Default,fla,0,0,0,,We'll let him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.12,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,逃がそう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.56,Default,fla,0,0,0,,The family tried to kill Nero like the Galassias wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.56,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,ファミリーはガラッシアの望み通り兄さんを消そうとした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.87,Default,fla,0,0,0,,but he was too sharp, and left town before we got to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.87,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,でも感のいい兄さんは さっさと町を出た
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.96,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Well, now! Isn't this a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.96,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,奇遇じゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:15.48,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Boy, let's have some more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:15.48,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ボーイ また遊ぼうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.77,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You're with Nero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.77,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,お前ネロとつるんでんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:30.40,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I see. You want a reward, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:30.40,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そうか ご褒美がほしいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.76,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Here's your reward. Don't be modest. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.76,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ほら ご褒美だ 遠慮すんな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:38.61,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:38.84,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,てめぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.21,Default,fan,0,0,0,,This kind of thing gets you hot, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.21,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,こういうの お前もぞくぞくするんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.29,Default,fan,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.99,Default,tig,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding! I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.99,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ふざけんな 一緒にすんな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:08.47,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Serpente. You got captured, huh? That's just sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:08.47,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,セルペンテ 捕まってたとは 様ねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.29,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You're Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.29,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,お前がネロか?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:13.97,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.13,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I've been hoping to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.13,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,会いたかったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.30,Default,fan,0,0,0,,How about we make a trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.30,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,此奴とそいつで交換だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.70,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You won't say no to that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.70,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,勿論 断らねぇよな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.15,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Hey, Gatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.15,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,おい ガット
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.67,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.67,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,お前からだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.93,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Us next. We'll put them down at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.93,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,次は俺たちだ 同時に置くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.42,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,同時に歩かせんぞ ほら いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.56,Default,fan,0,0,0,,We'll start them walking at the same time. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.64,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ほら いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:54.78,Default,fan,0,0,0,,That boy yesterday sure surprised me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:54.78,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,しかし 昨日のボーイには驚いたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.39,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Good man, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.39,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いい男たっだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.22,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.22,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.19,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.19,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.27,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Is it my imagination, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.27,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺の気のせいか?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.12,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Hey, Serpente.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.12,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,おぃ セルペンテ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.38,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You've lost a little weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.38,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,お前少し痩せたな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.76,Default,fan,0,0,0,,And your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.76,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,それによ お前の服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.55,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Oh, well. Keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.55,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,まぁ いい 歩け
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.33,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I thought I smelled something fishy about you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.33,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,道理でイカ臭ぇと思ったぜ ボーイ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.30,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.30,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,行け
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's the one who killed Vanno?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.27,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.07,Default,gat,0,0,0,,Serpente...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.07,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,セルペンテ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.44,Default,gat,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.44,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,チクショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.55,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You idiot. Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.55,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,馬鹿野郎 なんて顔してやがんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:22.00,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Now we can declare war on the Vanettis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:22.00,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,これで思う存分バネッティと戦争できるじゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.78,Default,bar,0,0,0,,They're going fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.78,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,飛ばしてるなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.30,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Frate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.30,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,フラテ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:58.51,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Brother, you have to leave the city as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:58.51,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,兄さん なるべく早く町を出てくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.27,Default,fla,0,0,0,,If anyone sees you, it won't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.27,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,誰かに見られじゃ まずいことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:05.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Isn't there any better way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:05.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,もう少しマシな手はねぇのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.71,Default,fla,0,0,0,,You won't die. Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.71,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,死なないだけマシだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.79,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Shall I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.79,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,一緒に行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.19,Default,fla,0,0,0,,No, you stay, Barbero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.19,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,いや バルベロは残ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.42,Default,fla,0,0,0,,We can't run the moonshine business without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.42,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,酒回りのことはお前がいなくちゃ回らない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.88,Default,bar,0,0,0,,But we can't let him go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.88,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,しかし 一人で行かせるわけには
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.95,Default,nero,0,0,0,,No worries. I'm just going for a quiet drive in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.95,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,心配するな 田舎をのんびりドライブしてくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:26.47,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why not take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:26.47,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺を連れてってくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.24,Default,av,0,0,0,,Fango seems to have committed my face to memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.24,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ファンゴに顔を覚えられたみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.17,Default,av,0,0,0,,I don't want to run into him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.17,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,また絡まれたら面倒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.02,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You can drive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.02,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,運転はできんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.89,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.89,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あぁ 問題ない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.12,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.12,通用720日文-ja,fla,0,0,0,,兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.20,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,此奴は結構使える
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:46.05,Default,bar,0,0,0,,By the way, did you decide on a place for the funeral?
